data.description: Like new DR Horton Bridgeport plan in the sought-after Rainier Ridge at Lipoma Firs community! Open concept great room/living rm W/gas fireplace & laminate hardwood floors. Kitchen offers a HUGE island W/barstool seating, granite counters, gas range, 6" glass tile backsplash, & SS appliances that STAY! Fresh interior paint! Desirable main floor bedroom & 3/4 bath! Utility room on main. Primary suite W/french door entry, relaxing 5-piece bath & huge WI closet! 3 additional bedrooms, bonus room/opt 6th bedroom, & a full bath upstairs. Large 2 car garage! Tankless water heater! Fully fenced yard W/patio & garden space! Huge community park W/sports courts, play structure, & covered seating area! Just minutes to shopping, restaurants, & schools!
